01:11.145 --> 01:19.998
So, after all, you have not given your lives and your struggle against sin, and have you forgotten the encouraging words God spoke to you as his children?

01:20.038 --> 01:27.890
He said, my child, don't make light of the Lord's discipline, and don't give up when he corrects you.

01:28.194 --> 01:33.347
