02:15.736 --> 02:21.541
But afterward, there will be a peaceful harvest of right living for those who are trained in this way.

02:22.662 --> 02:26.126
So take a new grip with your tired hands and strengthen your weak knees.

02:26.766 --> 02:32.752
Mark out a straight path for your feet so that those who are weak and lame will not fall but become strong.

02:33.914 --> 02:36.116
And work at living in peace with everyone.

02:37.057 --> 02:38.999
Work at living a holy life.

02:39.699 --> 02:42.482
For those who are not holy will not see the Lord.

02:42.562 --> 02:44.164
This is the word of God for the people of God.

02:44.204 --> 02:45.567
Thanks, pity God.

02:45.607 --> 02:53.799
Okay, I'm going to transition now to a different mic.

02:53.819 --> 02:54.801
I don't want to hold that for the whole time.

02:54.821 --> 02:56.363
Let's see if this works.

02:56.383 --> 02:56.503
Hello.

02:56.523 --> 02:58.687
I have all the faith and our wizard in the back.

02:59.307 --> 02:59.868
Dean's got it.

02:59.888 --> 03:00.229
We're good.

03:00.489 --> 03:01.030
Okay, excellent.

03:01.130 --> 03:01.691
Beautiful.

03:02.592 --> 03:03.314
All right, my friends.

03:03.714 --> 03:07.600
So again, if you missed it earlier, my name is my Beth.

03:07.640 --> 03:08.882
