03:34.949 --> 03:38.994
But before we do any of that this morning, I want to talk to you about music.

03:39.650 --> 03:46.558
And those of you who've heard me preach before know that I like to take the scenic route, but I promise we're going to get to our destination eventually.

03:46.598 --> 03:47.839
So just trust the process.

03:47.919 --> 03:48.019
Okay.

03:48.760 --> 03:49.701
So I adore music.

03:49.861 --> 03:52.104
I come from a music loving family.

03:52.124 --> 03:57.329
I probably have listened to some, at least one song every day of my life.

03:58.130 --> 04:02.335
If you went into the church office and you smell a candle and you hear music, that's me.

04:02.655 --> 04:02.775
Okay.

04:02.795 --> 04:04.537
Like I always have music going in the background.

04:04.577 --> 04:05.458
